---
title: Mexican Kumara & Veggie Bowl with Chilli Fried Eggs & Chunky Guac
description: Get ready to be bowled over by this bright, bold and saucy combination of flavours. With roasted veggies, a charred corn salsa, chunky smashed avocado and topped off with an oozy egg, this is a colourful taste of Mexico in an easy-to-eat, but hard-to-put-down package!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5be24263ae08b5659a7fcf52-e6f09660.jpg
